.DS_Store
__pycache__/

# Personal data — NEVER commit (public repo). CI gets these via Actions secrets.
candidate_profile.md
resume.md
resume.txt
shortlist.*

# ── Fork-owner customization ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Upstream never commits these so pulling upstream never creates merge conflicts.
# Fork owners: copy from *.example.json, customize, then commit to YOUR fork.
config.json
scoring_profile.json

# ── Scraped results & CI-generated data (unique per fork) ─────────────────────
# Each fork's CI writes its own results here; excluding from upstream prevents
# merge conflicts when fork owners pull upstream code improvements.
all_jobs.json
jobs.json
jobs.md
jobs.html
*_jobs.json
*_jobs.md
*_jobs.html
triage.html
workflow_runs.jsonl
scores.json
notified.json
checked_companies.json
